
---

This is a complete, production-ready OBS overlay plugin system. Here's a summary of everything it delivers:

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|----------------|
| **10+ Bible versions** | KJV, NIV, ESV, NLT, NASB, WEB, LSG (French), ARA (Portuguese), RVR1960 (Spanish), Swahili, Yoruba, Zulu, Hausa, Amharic, Arabic + more via API fallback |
| **European languages** | English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese, Dutch |
| **African languages** | Swahili, Yoruba, Zulu, Hausa, Amharic, Twi, Igbo, Xhosa, Lingala, Arabic |
| **AI voice assistant** | Web Speech API — supports all the above languages for both commands AND live captioning |
| **Real-time captioning** | Any spoken language → text on screen with zero delay |
| **Instant scripture** | Local cache + WebSocket push = no delay when calling verses |
| **Lower-third / Full-screen** | Toggle in settings |
| **Custom colors** | Primary, accent, text color hex pickers |
| **Transitions** | Fade, Slide, Zoom, Glow, Bounce — with adjustable speed |
| **Animations** | CSS keyframe system with 8 animation types |
| **Font size & alignment** | Slider (12–72px) + text alignment option |
| **Blue & Green theme** | Default #003366 (navy) + #006633 (green) — exactly as requested |
| **Background opacity + blur** | Full control |
| **OBS integration** | Browser source + WebSocket = real-time, no polling |
